doc.after: Biscayne National Park operates year round Camping is most practical in winter months when mosquitoes are less troublesome on the keys Private concessioners operate snorkeling and diving tours as well as reef tours in glass bottom boats Boat excursions to Boca Chita Adams and Elliott Keys are also available 61
